hc.server.msb

Class AnalysableRobotParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • hc.server.msb.AnalysableRobotParameter

  • public class AnalysableRobotParameter
extends Object
    this class is used to pass parameter between UI (includes Assistant) and Robot.
    it is helpful for server to analyze the parameter and know more about the relationship between business and user interface.

    it is recommended to be used in Robot.operate(long, Object) and the return object.

    Note :
    the instance is NOT recyclable, because server will analyst it background.
    See Also:
    Robot, Assistant
